title: Orange Chicken with Grand Marnier
ingredients: ['4 skinless, boneless chicken breast fillets', '250ml milk', '110g breadcrumbs', '80g parmigiano reggiano (parmesan), grated', '2 tablespoons chopped fresh parsley', '250ml olive oil', '1 orange, sliced into rounds', '250ml dry white wine', '125ml orange juice', '300ml chicken stock', '4 tablespoons brandy-based orange liqueur, such as Grand Marnier(R)']
